| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4485 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0bed136b-c3c7-5421-8b9d-1c2173c05eeb"
